Titolo: Monster Boy and the Cursed Kingdom

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Monster Boy and the Cursed Kingdom is a platform game developed by Game Atelier and published by FDG Entertainment. The game is a followup to Sega's Wonder Boy series, and was released for the Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One in December 2018, for Windows in July 2019, for Stadia in July 2020, Amazon Luna in February 2021, and PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S is set to release at a later date. In May 2020, Arc System Works announced their publishing handle of the game in Japan which is set to be released on August 6, 2020. It was generally well received by critics.

Genere: Platform 

Valutazione: 85
